Welcome to Pong! With power Ups!

ALL CODE INSIDE OF CODE BRANCH

instructions

each person has a paddle
player1 moves with w and s and starts on the left of the screen
player2 moves with up and down arrowkeys and starts on the right of the screen

a ball will spawn and bouce off of walls and paddles
the goal of the game is to bounce the ball in such a way the it gets past the other players paddle
if you do that you get one point
if the ball hits one of the coloured circles something will happen

BLUE: the opponents speed will drop
RED: both players speeds will drop
MAGENTA: the balls speed will increase

powerup effects last for 6 turns

once the score limit is reached the game is over and the person with the most amount of points wins the game
